</section>

<!-- Division of labour -->
<section class="container-x py-20 md:py-28">
    {{ sectionHead("The method", "Fine-tuning teaches behaviour. Retrieval supplies facts.", "The two are routinely conflated — and the conflation is where AI projects go wrong.") }}
